3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses deep learning techniques to achieve its objectives. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper involves the use of machine learning algorithms to train the model. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with the generation of realistic faces from stylized portraits.
